The '''[[Aargau/Legends|Aargau]] Medical Observer Corps''' was a neutral organization that was active during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The Observer Corps was tolerated by both sides of the conflict and allowed access to war-torn areas in order to investigate potential atrocities committed during the fighting.

